# ─── PERSONAL / RUNTIME DATA — must NEVER be committed ────────────────────
# Reference libraries + per-subject genomes/health data live in ~/.indaga
# (outside the repo). These patterns are defensive in case anything is ever
# created inside the working tree. The repo ships ZERO personal data.
/.indaga/
users/
data/
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.health-index.sqlite
*.vcf
*.vcf.gz
*.bcf
*.bam
*.cram
*.fastq
*.fastq.gz
*.gvcf
*.gvcf.gz
report*.html
